inSSIDer 3.1.2.1 Home Free
****************************************************************

ENGLISH DESCRIPTION
****************************************************************- Latest free version available (version 4 is paid)
- See info about all WiFi networks available to your computer/notebook: frequency, channel, network name (SSID), wifi board vendor, etc.
- Very useful for you to choose the best channel for your WiFi network in order to avoid interferences and overlaps from other networks.
Tip: the best channels for WiFi are 1, 6 and 11, because these don't overlap other channels. But you should examine whether there are already many computers using these channels.
- Oficial site: <a href=" http://www.metageek.net/" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://www.metageek.net/</a>
